itemLabel: Richard Wyndham-Quin, 6th Earl of Dunraven and Mount-Earl

wikipedia_page.main: Richard Southwell Windham Robert Wyndham-Quin, 6th Earl of Dunraven and Mount-Earl,  (18 May 1887 – 28 August 1965) was an Irish peer. The son of Windham Wyndham-Quin, 5th Earl of Dunraven and Mount-Earl, he succeeded to the Earldom in 1952 on the death of his father.
